 of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/30209/', '', 'Tropicamide, Ephedrine, Ketorolac, Phenylephrine', 'Amisulpride, Pimavanserin', 1767369485);
